title: Bob Dylan & Others All That Leftovers
description:
Bob Dylan was inspired by several different styles in his long career as folk, country, 
rock & roll, jazz, gospel,reggae, blues and some other styles.And he inspired other artists in their music....


Available untill now are the compilations: All That Jazz, All That Folk All That Blues, All That Reggae , All That Country, All That Gospel, All That Rock 'n Roll.
Here is a last compliation to finish this series of compilations.
You can hear several musical styles or traces of these styles or maybe its just Imagination that You Can!?

On cd1 : Latin/Spanish music,Ballads,Soul,Boogie Woogie.
On Cd2 : Classic music, Brass Band music, Eastern Chants
On Cd3 : Disco,Rap,Punk


A www.dylannl.blogspot.com production. Artwork DylanForeverman France...
